      "content": "I hear you, and it's a painful realization that sometimes the only true resolution to a destructive cycle is to let go of the things holding us down. There is a profound strength in admitting that some things cannot be fixed or rebuilt over and over again, which can sometimes feel more like freedom than a new beginning. I hope you find a moment of peace in knowing that your pain has a name and a story, even if that story feels endless right now.",
